st year graduate students in mathematics. Our goal is to introduce basic concepts from deep learning in a rigorous mathematical fashion, e.g introduce mathematical definitions of deep neural networks (DNNs), loss functions, the backpropagation algorithm, etc. We attempt to identify for each concept the simplest setting that minimizes technicalities but still contains the key mathematics.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aDeep learning (Machine learning)xMathematics. 4aFaltungsneuronale Netze. 4aKünstliche Neuronale Netze. 4aMaschinelles Lernen. 4aTiefes Lernen. 7aCOMPUTERS / Intelligence (AI) & Semantics.2bisacsh  aMachine Learning, Deep Learning, Artificial Neural Networks (ANNs), Regression, Deep Neural Networks (DNNs),.1 aJabin, Pierre-Emmanuel, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2023 Englishz978311131912408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2023z9783111318165oZDB-23-DEI0 cEPUBz97831110258030 cprintz978311102431840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311102555140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111025551423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111025551/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  a978-3-11-131912-4  EBOOK PACKAGE Engineering, Computer Sciences 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_CH